2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper specifically mentions the development of an "artificial intelligence capable of driving autonomously," indicating a focus on AI. 
3. cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses the software and systems engineering process used to develop the autonomous driving software. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the development of a complex system (an autonomous driving vehicle) and the need for an adaptable engineering process. 
5. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper may involve computer vision techniques for the vehicle to perceive its environment and make decisions.
